text: Palmapampa Airport is an airport serving the town of Palmapampa in the Ayacucho Region of Peru. The runway is just off the AY-101 Santa Rosa - Samugari Road. ==See also== * * *Transport in Peru *List of airports in Peru ==References== ==External links== *OpenStreetMap - Palmapampa Category:Airports in Peru Category:Buildings and structures in Ayacucho Region
